              "text": "[i]Special Modpack made for [b][REDACTED][/b].\n\n[i]Concept, design, custom art, scripting, and more all by Caigan.\n\nSpecial thanks to the Forge and mod devs who make this all possible.\n\nPlease enjoy the pack, and if you don\u0027t, may you find one works for you!\n                                        -Caigan",
