          "feature": {
            "class": "joshie.enchiridion.gui.book.features.FeatureText",
            "properties": {
              "text": "[i]Roughly once a year, I try to take a week or two off my current larger projects to work on something smaller. Specifically : a modpack for one of my communities.\n\nThis is one of those modpacks. \n\nUnlike the previous ones, this one I started with the goal of sharing my work with everyone.\n\nThe ulterior motive of doing this was also to try something different than what I am doing with The Ferret Business, and learn some of the new tools and mods that I hope to use in my next pack! (Yes, it will be The Ferret Business 2, some time down the line!)\n\nThis modpack will not have giant questlines or super heavily gated progression. There are some of both, but only to provide some loose goals for players to strive for.\n\nRead on for the LORE and some guides!",
