          "width": 175.0,
          "height": 74.0,
          "feature": {
            "class": "joshie.enchiridion.gui.book.features.FeatureText",
            "properties": {
              "text": "The Cleansing is what we call the final act of the Ancient One\u0027s summoning.\n\nMany years ago, The Cult of All sought to cleanse the world of all evil, and danced with the devil. The devil were two of the Ancient Ones, elder gods who once lived in this reality.\n\nThey were summoned in diminished form, but with the help of the Cult, they regained their full power, and granted their wishes.\n\nBut like the proverbial genie, the wish is taken literally, figuratively, and to the letter all at once.",
              "size": 0.9
            }
          },
          "isLocked": false,
          "isHidden": false,
          "layerIndex": 2
        },
        {
          "xPos": 35,
          "yPos": 19,
          "width": 175.0,
          "height": 12.0,
          "feature": {
            "class": "joshie.enchiridion.gui.book.features.FeatureText",
            "properties": {
              "text": "[b][u]THE CLEANSING[/u]",
              "size": 1.8000002
            }
          },
          "isLocked": false,
          "isHidden": false,
          "layerIndex": 3
        },
        {
          "xPos": 234,
          "yPos": 20,
          "width": 175.0,
          "height": 74.0,
          "feature": {
            "class": "joshie.enchiridion.gui.book.features.FeatureText",
            "properties": {
              "text": "The Ancient Ones swept across the land, decimating everyone they came across. Many would be heroes, wizards, armies, all fell to their eldritch power.\n\nSome hid. Some survived the deadly war path. The lucky ones survived the Cleansing in tiny pockets in the wilderness. Those in the cities, however, did not.\n\nAlong with the majority of civilization itself, the Ancient Ones also destroyed what knowledge they could with their otherworldly powers. Knowledge gained by generations was \u0027destroyed\u0027 and lost to the world.\n\nWith the world cleansed of evil, both living and that created by it, the Ancient Ones left.",
              "size": 0.9
            }
          },
          "isLocked": false,
          "isHidden": false,
