        {
          "xPos": 25,
          "yPos": 30,
          "width": 175.0,
          "height": 74.0,
          "feature": {
            "class": "joshie.enchiridion.gui.book.features.FeatureText",
            "properties": {
              "text": "Two beacons of hope survived The Cleansing intact. Warned early of The Cult of All\u0027s plans, two cities gathered all the power and knowledge they could and created a barrier to hide themselves from the Ancient Ones.\n\nThey saved as many nearby villages as they could and warned everyone else, offering the knowledge of how to save more lives, but no one believed them until it was too late.\n\nFerretopia and its sister city Port Burda remained, forming the FOGCraft group. \n\nAnd you, Engineer of FOGCraft, are the best hope to rebuild Civilization.\n\nYou shall help enact The Plan.",
              "size": 0.9
            }
