          "height": 84.0,
          "feature": {
            "class": "joshie.enchiridion.gui.book.features.FeatureText",
            "properties": {
              "text": "Welcome to the Overworld post Cleansing, Engineer. We\u0027ve waited years, constructing the FOGLiner and the research we\u0027d need to rebuild civilization. And now it is time to enact The Plan.\n\nThe Plan can be summed up in a few simple steps, Engineer : \n\n[b]1)[/b] Gather materials and establish a base of operations.\n[b]2)[/b] Gear up to protect yourself.\n[b]3)[/b] Secure every Village you find, and clean out as many haunted Lost City structures as possible.\n[b]4)[/b] Build a Rail Station in every Village and Lost City, connecting as many of them as possible into a giant rail network.",
              "size": 0.9
            }
          },
